name: (prototype) Congratulations, You Have Died!
description:
HINTS: #1- you don't have to enter a code if you're just trying to spam wrong answers. just hit the enter button. #2- if you don't see it, look in the black square near the bottom left for the "correct" code, it's in kind of a dark grey color.

Possible trigger warnings: Flashing lights (maybe?), screen shake

Made for Mini Jam 96: FATE, with the limitation of 'losing is winning'.
